  "texts": [
    "The deck is made up of cards numbered 1 through 5, further divided into five different colors.",
    "Players are working together to create these numbered sequences (1 through 5) for each of the five colors.",
    "Each card played provides 1 point, and the goal is to obtain all 25 points (5 colors with 5 cards each) by completing the sequence for each color.",
    "The three actions a player can take include playing a card, discarding a card, and giving a hint (reveal) to a teammate.",
    "The challenge is that players cannot see their own cards."
  ],
